data.description: Introducing an exceptional investment opportunity, this solid brick two-flat stands as a testament to both charm and upgraded appeal. Boasting a total of two units, the property offers versatility and promise for buyers of all backgrounds. The first floor presents a cozy yet spacious three-bedroom, one-bathroom unit. Ascend to the second floor to find another well-appointed three-bedroom, one-bathroom apartment. Situated just blocks from I-290 and the Blue Line Train, convenience is key in this sought-after location. Whether you're a first-time buyer or a seasoned investor, this property offers endless possibilities. With both units receiving approximately $1,400 each, the property yields a total monthly income of $2,800.
